[[xfer_plugin]]
Xfer plugin
~~~~~~~~~~~

Xfer plugin brings:

* direct chat (between two hosts, without server): for example "DCC Chat" via
  IRC plugin
* file transfer, for example "DCC" via IRC plugin

Options (xfer.conf)
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

